      "content": "it doesn't feel like \"shifting\" though. it feels like a total collapse. every paper i published, every lecture i gave... it was all based on a mistake. i can't just \"grow\" from this. the person i was is dead. there's just this empty shell of a person left who's embarrassed to even look in the mirror. i feel like i'm just playing a part in a life that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
